    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择拥有独特技能的蜂后，招募工匠，在战场上建造强大的炮塔。装备配件，施放毁灭性法术，在这款充满个性与混乱的 Roguelike 塔防游戏中守卫你的蜂巢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一轮游戏都将探索充满趣味彩蛋、陷阱和独特机制的地图。面对难以预测的Boss，解锁配件与法术卡牌，彻底改变战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理资源，制定防御策略，尝试数百万种组合方式，抵御源源不断的僵蜂大军。<strong>在僵蜂末日中生存下来！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/4a790fb0b06299a0b67772948f2fd5c3.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/255a4d0c6b2b95c6fe86693c2d08b2d1.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/255a4d0c6b2b95c6fe86693c2d08b2d1.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/255a4d0c6b2b95c6fe86693c2d08b2d1.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 选择各具特色的蜂后<br>• 招募拥有不同炮塔与技能的工匠<br>• 建造具有特殊效果与功能的炮塔<br>• 收集配件与法术卡牌，打造荒诞强力的组合</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/f4662d199fd78394db23e097c019b08c.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/bcc41157ddebef8d4868bbc11f8470b2.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/bcc41157ddebef8d4868bbc11f8470b2.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/bcc41157ddebef8d4868bbc11f8470b2.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 应对行为多变的敌人<br>• 挑战拥有独特机制与阶段的Boss<br>• 在蜂群、陷阱和动态事件中生存下来</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/44f5648d5816afc9a26a27a517936706.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9fb607212232a49983524fce8e0db1a4.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9fb607212232a49983524fce8e0db1a4.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9fb607212232a49983524fce8e0db1a4.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 探索被混乱吞噬的区域，体验独特视觉风格与障碍机制<br>• 发现隐藏彩蛋、秘密与趣味互动<br>• 重建梅尔托比亚大陆，让这片土地再次安全</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9adbcd128721d6a7e06731e6b376b744.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9bb4c03eb2ab1701ca99f021ef5a832e.avif?t=1758895362\" width=301 height=163 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/4bbdcf89d946504eb713fc1934dace29.avif?t=1758895362\" width=301 height=163 /></span></p>",
